result.name: Genome Wide Association Study and Genomic Selection of Amino Acid Concentrations in Soybean Seeds
result.description: This is report of GWAS and GS of amino acid contents in cultivated soybean seeds. The results are anticipated to facilitate marker assisted selection and GS of nutritional traits in soybean, gene identification and cloning.
result.center: National Soybean Improvement Center Shijiazhuang Sub-Center
